        "datePublished": "2020-06-19T04:00:36.000Z",
        "description": "This is very much like Krest&reg; Bitter Lemon (found in Africa) or Schweppes&reg; Bitter Lemon (found in Europe). Unfortunately there is nothing comparable found in the USA, but this comes pretty darn close! This is the perfect thirst quencher for a blistering hot day!",
        "prepTime": "P0DT0H10M",
